title: Roasting Each Other With Smosh Memes
author: Smosh Games
description:
We’re getting anonymously roasted with memes and it’s our job to figure out who made ‘em! Check us out every Monday, Wednesday, Friday at https://twitch.tv/smoshgames

This video was shot with a very limited crew. All cast & crew followed all CDC and California COVID-19 precautions and filming guidelines.

Punch that bell icon so you'll know when we add a new episode!
